Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}腾空而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:40.89,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}定要接近那片光明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:45.01,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}触及希望燎原的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:49.52,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾经目睹的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.89,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}它的尽头通向未来
