Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:09.47,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂 欢 节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵方法你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系统很简单 没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这吗 可别搞坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 抬起手臂看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系统已经掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报支援系统在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过计算机进行的战况分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看着办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样移动到环流银河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 要安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在环上开出洞来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示当前位置 固定坐标值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快重新站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求情报支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像游泳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体放松就能浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不会游泳就先说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到机体会如此不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 宇宙中没有海嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 我们去吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是你点的少女套餐和紫菜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要这些就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他好吃的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的事不用沮丧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德你可以再放轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松？要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大玩特玩一场就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天开始就是祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得表现出觉得好吃的表情才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好吃的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 你还没换衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话 好男人都会被抢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 帅哥在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算霸占人家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一起去参观祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕鱼的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机可单独执行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉可继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这次开自己的人形机器人来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机并非人形机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是Machine Caliber-K6821
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿参加捕鱼任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员雷德少尉正在视察祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那小子不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始执行海洋生物的捕捉任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拿网去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你之前完全沉下海了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber在替我干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来稍微陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你不知道怎么花钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这次我就特别请你搓一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当作示范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫菜面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特选晚餐两人份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 特选晚餐两人份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 思乡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到宇宙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有地图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的生活如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和大家之间的距离 很远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃紫菜面包当然是这样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都讨厌紫菜面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙太没存在感了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没存在感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 就没什么想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回归同盟的战线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指在你现在所在的地方 在这艘船上想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己想要什么都不知道 怎么能得到别人的信赖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我合伙打捞船只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打捞船只？工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个破废铁一定能捞到大宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算赚到钱 工资也花不完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 赚到钱就去吃好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等赚到更多的钱 就去搞艘更好的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱放在手里也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要像这样去实现自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现…自己的欲望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢着挖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢着挖人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要合伙的话 应该找专职的我才是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你培养成一流的船只打捞师的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打捞船只的事 我不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很简单 我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不懂的地方只管问就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不知道怎么做 那就有样学样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别听她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合伙 好吃的要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你如何辨别潮汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有资质 很快就能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合伙的话 好酒随便你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子还得教你游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子的屁股随便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你从刚刚开始就很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 你这贝壳屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是贝壳屁股啊 你这旱鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是旱鸭子 只是不会潜水罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 这是您的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯 人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是章鱼罢了 很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是光看到这小章鱼就吃惊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上鲸乌贼还不得吓趴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼 能吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机请求驾驶员雷德少尉支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力振荡 展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.85,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(594,650)}Gravity Waver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也好 你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在想些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营养学上没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法应对目前情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机请求雷德少尉支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都成肉泥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 用网来捞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看别人是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要尽可能大的网
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及请求其他人形机器人的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得意个啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饱饱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电：我只能帮你到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 索敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围检测到能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险级别：低
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是光幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环流银河消失的时候便会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛子还得好好练习才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习？ 艾米 你练过舞蹈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看 艾米 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就当作刚刚的回礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 雷德哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚钱 付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起 吃好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拿到的报酬是扶持了别人的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扶持了别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人邀请我去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Chamber一起打捞船只
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为海里沉着很多东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许可以知道这颗星球以前发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去打捞船只
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你肯定会去皮尼欧那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有些东西 希望贝罗兹教我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这台人形机器人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是好像很快就会没东西可教了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 我想学到更多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 这个也中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是宝贝 要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌影 需要迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次确认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固有反应解析完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖然性99.7％。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认定对象为希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始交战 歼灭希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
